Zenbite contributors
====================

Project lead and primary maintainer
-----------------------------------

* Oliver Petz <oliverpetz805@gmail.com>  (GitHub: @olivenda)

Contributors
------------

Zenbite is built by everyone who has sent a patch. Add yourself in your first PR
(any format: name, GitHub handle, or both).

The canonical record of contributions is the git log:

    git shortlog -sne
